last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 6
last_episode_to_air.overview: As Andy and Conrad both process potentially career-launching opportunites, the boys all take stock of how far they've come. Andy and Simon run into each other for the first time in months. Freddy and Andy have some unfinished business to take care of, and Andy finally goes to therapy to confront the past few months.

name: Mess
overview: Soon after moving to New York City to pursue his dream of becoming an actor, 22-year-old Andy is diagnosed with HIV. Now, Andy and his three best friends must come to terms with his life-changing news while struggling to survive life in the city.
